---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Shopify development" description="Themes, extensions, integrations, and Shopify builds—done with performance and review requirements in mind.">
  <section class="container-pad py-14 sm:py-20">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="reveal" data-reveal>
          <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1 text-xs text-white/70">
            Themes · Extensions · Integrations · Automation
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Shopify development</h1>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-white/70">
            We build Shopify themes, app extensions, and automation—especially around personalization, fulfillment, and high-conversion product page UX.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Request quote</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/products/zenmerch">See ZenMerch</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/services/webapp-development">Web apps</a>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs text-white/70">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1">OS 2.0</span>
            <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1">Theme app extensions</span>
            <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1">Checkout UI extensions</span>
            <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1">Webhooks</span>
            <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1">ERP / POD / shipping</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="card reveal p-6" data-reveal>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold">What we can deliver</div>
          <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 text-sm text-white/70">
            <li>Theme updates and OS2 migration</li>
            <li>Theme app blocks and storefront UX</li>
            <li>Checkout extensibility (where available)</li>
            <li>Custom apps and admin tooling</li>
            <li>Integrations (ERP, POD, shipping)</li>
            <li>Automation and operational tooling</li>
            <li>Review-ready documentation and handoff</li>
          </ul>
          <img class="mt-5 w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02]" src="/images/services/shopify.png" alt="" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-pad pb-14 sm:pb-20">
    <div class="reveal" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What we build</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-sm text-white/65">
        Shopify work that’s designed to be maintainable—so you can keep improving without fragile theme edits or operational surprises.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Themes + OS 2.0 migration</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
            Upgrade older themes, modernize your design system, and keep templates clean with section-based architecture.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Extensions + conversion UX</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
            Theme app blocks, cart enhancements, and checkout extensibility—implemented with performance and Shopify requirements in mind.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Integrations + automation</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
            Webhooks, exports, and sync layers that connect Shopify to fulfillment, POD, shipping, and internal systems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-pad pb-14 sm:pb-20">
    <div class="card reveal p-8 md:p-10" data-reveal>
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Capabilities</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-sm text-white/65">
            The building blocks we use for reliable Shopify implementations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary hidden sm:inline-flex" href="/contact">Request quote</a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Theme development</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
            Section architecture, performance tuning, responsive polish, and conversion-friendly product page UX.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Theme app extensions</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
            App blocks and embed flows designed to minimize theme edits and reduce compatibility risk.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Checkout extensibility</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
            Checkout UI extensions and post-purchase experiences where supported by your plan and storefront setup.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">APIs + data flows</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
            Shopify Admin APIs, Storefront APIs, and predictable data contracts for downstream systems.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Webhooks + fulfillment ops</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
            Order sync, production-ready exports, and webhook-driven workflows for batching and automation.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Performance + quality</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
            Clean JS/CSS, sane app-script footprints, and practical accessibility/QA so updates don’t break your storefront.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Book a call</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/services/website-development">Need a marketing site too?</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-pad pb-14 sm:pb-20">
    <div class="reveal" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Our process</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-sm text-white/65">
        We align on the fastest safe path to ship—then iterate with clear checkpoints.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-5">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">1) Discovery</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/65">Goals, constraints, theme/app setup, and success metrics.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">2) Audit</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/65">Performance, compatibility risks, and workflow mapping.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">3) Build</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/65">Theme/extension work in incremental, reviewable slices.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">4) QA</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/65">Device coverage, edge cases, and regression checks.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">5) Launch</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/65">Deploy, verify metrics, and document the handoff.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-pad pb-14 sm:pb-20">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="reveal" data-reveal>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Timeline expectations</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-sm text-white/65">
            Shopify timelines depend on theme complexity, app footprint, and review speed. Most projects land in one of these ranges.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 grid gap-3">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Quick fixes + enhancements</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/60">~ 2–5 days</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
                Small theme changes, section tweaks, app block placement improvements, and performance cleanup.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Theme refresh / OS 2.0 migration</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/60">~ 2–4 weeks</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
                New templates, a cleaner component set, better performance, and a safer long-term theme structure.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Custom app or integration</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/60">~ 4–10+ weeks</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
                More complex builds: admin tooling, multiple systems, automation, and robust monitoring.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="card reveal p-6" data-reveal>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold">What we need from you</div>
          <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 text-sm text-white/70">
            <li>Store access (collaborator) and theme details</li>
            <li>Goals + priorities (conversion, speed, new feature, etc.)</li>
            <li>List of installed apps (especially anything touching PDP/cart/checkout)</li>
            <li>Integration credentials (ERP/POD/shipping) or sandbox access</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 text-sm text-white/65">
            If you have a slow product page, send us the URL. We’ll identify the biggest performance wins and the likely cause (apps vs theme).
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-pad pb-20">
    <div class="card reveal p-8 md:p-10" data-reveal>
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-sm text-white/65">
            Common questions about themes, app blocks, Shopify requirements, and ongoing support.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <details class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold text-white/90">Do you work with our existing theme?</summary>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
              Yes. We can improve an existing theme, migrate to OS 2.0, or help you adopt a modern base theme—while keeping your brand intact.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold text-white/90">Can you build custom Shopify apps?</summary>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
              Yes. We build app extensions, admin tooling, and integrations. If your goal is product personalization, we also offer
              <a class="text-white/80 hover:text-white" href="/products/zenmerch">ZenMerch</a>.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold text-white/90">How do you handle Shopify review requirements?</summary>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
              We favor OS 2.0 app blocks and clear documentation, and we avoid risky patterns that can break theme compatibility. Requirements vary by
              project, so we’ll align early on expectations and constraints.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold text-white/90">Do you help with performance?</summary>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
              Yes. We audit app/script footprint and theme rendering, prioritize the highest-impact fixes, and keep changes measured and reversible.
            </div>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-semibold text-white/90">Do you provide ongoing support?</summary>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">
              Yes. After launch we can help with fixes, improvements, new sections, and operational automation. Or we can do a clean handoff if you prefer.
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Get a Shopify quote</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/products/zenmerch/docs">Read ZenMerch docs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

